  "description": "<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t<img src=\"https://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/07/12/9256efea90aec6a54479d43a9d4bc8c2.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t<strong>114. Some technologies do indeed improve at such a predictable pace that they obey simple formulae such as Moore&rsquo;s law, which acts as a battle plan for the semiconductor industry. </strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t<strong>【结构分析】</strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t本句结构清晰，主句为Some technologies do indeed improve at such a predictable pace that they obey simple formulae such as Moore&rsquo;s law，使用了such&hellip;that&hellip;结构；关系代词which引导定语从句which acts as a battle plan for the semiconductor industry，修饰前面的整个句子，which在从句中作主语。<br />\n\t<strong>【词汇】<br />\n\t</strong>formula n. 公式<br />\n\tact as 扮演<br />\n\tbattle plan ［比喻］设计图纸</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t<strong>【参考译文】</strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t的确，有些技术的进步是以一种可预测的节奏进行着，它们遵循摩尔定律般简单的公式，好比是半导体工业的设计图纸。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1186676/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1186676\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1190738/\">为什么咖啡越来越贵？原来罪魁祸首在这</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p825931/\">有声双语美文：无法看清现状能力就没有价值</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1190636/\">黄老板客串《权力的游戏》，权迷们不高兴了</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1159092/\">有声双语美文：未曾体验，又怎能读懂人生？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1172988/\">Nice to meet you的其他表达方式</a></li><li style=\"margin